      <title>经历了 2010 年以来最糟糕的一年后，法国股市将继续下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-07/french-stock-pain-set-to-continue-after-worst-year-since-2010</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经过数月的低迷表现后，法国股市本周迎来了强劲反弹。但这可能只是昙花一现，因为法国的政治危机将持续下去，而该国紧张的公共财政将使长期投资者望而却步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-07/french-stock-pain-set-to-continue-after-worst-year-since-2010</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 07 Dec 2024 09:11:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
