      <title>黄金价格飙升后中国上月恢复黄金购买</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-07/china-resumes-buying-gold-reserves-in-nov-after-6-month-halt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国央行 11 月份增加了黄金储备，结束了黄金价格升至历史新高后六个月的黄金购买暂停状态。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-07/china-resumes-buying-gold-reserves-in-nov-after-6-month-halt</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 07 Dec 2024 02:03:15 GMT</pubDate>
